<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for a Busy Week</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Apr 24, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Father,
</p>

 <p>
We live in a world <br></br>
with walls both <br></br>
visible and invisible; <br></br>
some protect us from harm, <br></br>
and others protect <br></br>
us from inconvenience, <br></br>
hearing only the voices <br></br>
that reinforce our fears.
</p>

 <p>
Open a window in the walls, <br></br>
so that we may hear the voice <br></br>
of the one who needs to be heard, <br></br>
who speaks in a still, small voice <br></br>
so often drowned out by our noisy lives.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>




